data.title: Thoroughbred Horse Racing in Southern California
data.meta_description: Santa Anita Park is a Thoroughbred racetrack in Arcadia, California. It offers some of the prominent horse racing events in the United States.
data.text:
You must be 18 or older to gamble on horse racing in California.

Problem Gambling? Help is available. If you, or someone you know, is concerned about compulsive gambling, call the National Council on Problem Gambling at 1.800.522.4700, or visit www.ncpgambling.org online.

Although every effort is made to ensure the accuracy of the information presented, details on this website are subject to change and cancellation. Santa Anita Park accepts no liability for errors.
